static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160195650/image_160195650.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160195650/image_160195650.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160195650/image_160195650.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160195650/image_160195650.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Juanmonino</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <blockquote> <p> </p> <p><em>How does an old investor reminisce about his first big win?</em></p> <p><em>\"Back in my day, we used to call that a \"retirement plan,\" now it's just a good Tuesday.\" - Unknown.</em></p> </blockquote> <p>One of the coolest things</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160195650/image_160195650.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745149-retirement-ready-income-5-dividend-gems-id-buy-if-i-were-65", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 15:30:00"}, {"id": "4745299", "title": "Market Meltdown: What Changed?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1215525233/image_1215525233.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Candlestick stock market chart falling prices drop down from global economic and financial crisis\" data-id=\"1215525233\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1215525233/image_1215525233.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1215525233/image_1215525233.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1215525233/image_1215525233.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1215525233/image_1215525233.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1215525233/image_1215525233.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1215525233/image_1215525233.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1215525233/image_1215525233.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1215525233/image_1215525233.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">coffeekai/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Why the shock and surprise?</h2> <p>What has changed in the statement? Only two things: the actual Fed Funds rate (which went down 1/4%), and one member of the committee became more hawkish. Amazingly, this took 2.58% off the Dow Jones Industrials (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1215525233/image_1215525233.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745299-market-meltdown-what-changed", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 15:20:00"}, {"id": "4745285", "title": "Overvaluation And Uncertainty Is A Path To Correction In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156920196/image_2156920196.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"2025 Over Financial Bar Graph Background\" data-id=\"2156920196\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"978px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156920196/image_2156920196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156920196/image_2156920196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156920196/image_2156920196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156920196/image_2156920196.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156920196/image_2156920196.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156920196/image_2156920196.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156920196/image_2156920196.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156920196/image_2156920196.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">MicroStockHub/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>For 2024, I correctly predicted a 20% up year for the S&amp;P 500 (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPX\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SPX</a></span>) and Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) to $100,000. My conviction on these ideas were very high confidence.</p> <p><strong><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4744378-stock-market-euphoria-to-100000-bitcoin-what-i-got-right-and-wrong-in-2024\">Stock Market Euphoria To $100,000 Bitcoin, What I Got Right</a></strong></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156920196/image_2156920196.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745285-overvaluation-uncertainty-path-to-correction-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 15:08:46"}, {"id": "4745169", "title": "3 Of The Biggest Lessons Of My Investing Career", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/493189993/image_493189993.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rear view of boy with raised hand in class\" data-id=\"493189993\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1069px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/493189993/image_493189993.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/493189993/image_493189993.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/493189993/image_493189993.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/493189993/image_493189993.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/493189993/image_493189993.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/493189993/image_493189993.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/493189993/image_493189993.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/493189993/image_493189993.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>My parents divorced when I was three years old, and I was raised by a single hard-working mother.</p> <p>She worked two jobs (three during Christmas) to make sure that our family had the necessities (roof, shelter, and clothing).</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_imag